      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is said that there are words before which a plosive</l>
<l>is inserted after the word denoting place-relationship.<note
              place="foot">E.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">mī.p-pal. 250-2</foreign> deal with non-case relationship.</note></l>
